{"tid":1744533,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"{認真}真心覺得班狗好可憐.......","createTime":"2019-11-21T19:18:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T04:06:56.000Z","uid":228924,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f1db3b5e44d39a81175d353d8275999354e132af","tid":1744533,"uid":228924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T19:18:58.000Z","msg":"同你哋比？<br />\n<br />\n唔撚係呱，你哋英文都唔識多隻<br />\n<br />\n講真！問你&rdquo;<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">小熊維尼</span></span>&rdquo;英文點串你都唔撚識啦<br />\n<br />\n唔好以為做警察好撚型<br />\n<br />\n你哋都係無獨立思考嘅<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">傀儡</span></span>嚟架咋柒頭<br />\n<br />\n你哋班垃圾咪又係淨係識聽上司order做嘢<br />\n同埋做隻聽話嘅狗，仲識做啲乜？<br />\n<br />\n我知你哋最撚中意係微博開啲垃圾po博同情<br />\n<br />\n見到啲大陸人留言講兩句支持下你哋就係咁攞嚟打飛機🤡<br />\n<br />\n其實真心覺得你哋好可憐<br />\n身為香港人但係無香港人支持真係好可悲<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港！<br />\n時代革命！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jtTUp8g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjtTUp8g.png&h=839ea183&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c45c3ff75d1c5d7040e5d092e68687393a35fb0a","tid":1744533,"uid":228924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T19:19:39.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"cca4608ed8e4396f101c3c8165c3ac75b78db693","tid":1744533,"uid":228924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T19:19:50.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"d5e801c62e1ce3743254fb8b3f5984e955cafcd3","tid":1744533,"uid":39751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T19:19:57.000Z","msg":"打個靚飛機先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f86303bf99b60e148373c5cb7a7899e2a0f9b16f","tid":1744533,"uid":228924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-1